column2: Everyone with a little bit of common sense can see from all the evidence that are accessible to the public that all the evidence that the Court choose to close their eyes on are all the ones proving "her" guilty. Really? In any other ordinary lawsuit the neutrality of the judge would be immediately questioned. Why not here? And again, the neutrality of the judge really is questionable here. So, I say, give Johnny Depp a REAL FAIR trial, with a REAL neutral judge and we'll see how things turn out then.
